---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-primary-500">
  <!-- Two-column grid: orange text left, dog photo right -->
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">

    <!-- LEFT: Orange panel with text -->
    <div class="relative flex items-center bg-primary-500 z-10">
      <!-- Decorative circles -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-80 h-80 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-20 left-20 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-700/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Curved edge that overlaps onto the photo -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 -right-16 bottom-0 w-32 bg-primary-500 hidden md:block" style="border-radius: 0 50% 50% 0;" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-16 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-28 max-w-xl ml-auto">

        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-sm font-medium px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 border border-white/30">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          Abrigo sem fins lucrativos
        </div>

        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Dá uma Segunda
          <span class="text-primary-100">Oportunidade</span>
          a um Cão
        </h1>

        <!-- Subtext -->
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-primary-100 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Cada cão que chega ao nosso abrigo carrega uma história de abandono.
          Juntos podemos mudar o seu destino. Encontra o teu companheiro de vida e
          dá-lhe o lar que merece.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/caes"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 bg-white text-primary-700 font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:bg-primary-50 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 group"
          >
            Conhece os Nossos Cães
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 10a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h10.638L10.23 5.29a.75.75 0 111.04-1.08l5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 010 1.08l-5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 11-1.04-1.08l4.158-3.96H3.75A.75.75 0 013 10z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/adocao"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 border-2 border-white/60 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white transition-all duration-200"
          >
            Adoção
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust indicators -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-2 mt-10 text-primary-100 text-sm font-medium">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-200" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Adoção responsável
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-200" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Vacinados e desparasitados
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-200" aria-hidden="true">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Apoio pós-adoção
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: Dog photo -->
    <div class="relative hidden md:block">
      <img
        src="/images/hero-dog.jpg"
        alt="Cão do abrigo CAPA a receber carinho"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        style="object-position: 40% center;"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Mobile: dog photo strip -->
  <div class="block md:hidden h-80 -mt-1" aria-hidden="false">
    <img
      src="/images/hero-dog.jpg"
      alt="Cão do abrigo CAPA a receber carinho"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      style="object-position: 40% 25%;"
      loading="eager"
    />
  </div>

</section>

<!-- Wave divider sits OUTSIDE the hero, spans full width, overlaps the bottom edge -->
<div class="relative z-20 -mt-6" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full block" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="M0 48L1440 48L1440 0C1200 32 960 48 720 48C480 48 240 32 0 0L0 48Z" fill="#faf6f2"/>
  </svg>
</div>
